(2259, 2081, 'METAS', 'http://files.spip.org/spip-zone/metas-spip3.png', '001.005.000', '1.2.0', '[3.0.0;3.1.*]', '3.0,3.1', '<multi>\n[en]This plugin makes possible to create and edit the META data for articles and rubriques of SPIP site.\n[fr]Gestion des métas <code>title</code>, <code>description</code> et <code>keywords</code> des articles et rubriques de SPIP, et mise en exergue de mots importants.\n[ru]Плагин позволяет создавать и редактировать META заголовки для страниц и разделов сайта. Перевод плагина - http://www.aloha.kiev.ua.\n</multi>', 'a:2:{i:1;a:3:{s:3:"nom";s:27:"Quentin de Serres-Justiniac";s:3:"url";s:36:"http://contrib.spip.net/?auteur10451";s:4:"mail";s:0:"";}i:2;a:3:{s:3:"nom";s:15:"Olivier Gendrin";s:3:"url";s:35:"http://contrib.spip.net/?auteur1343";s:4:"mail";s:0:"";}}', '', '', '', 'http://contrib.spip.net/Metas', '', '', 'test', 3, 'a:3:{s:9:"necessite";a:0:{}s:9:"librairie";a:0:{}s:7:"utilise";a:0:{}}', '2015-12-09 15:44:15', '2015-12-09 15:44:15', 1, 'metas-spip3.zip', 25220, '2015-12-23 14:09:18', '_plugins_/metas/trunk', 'a:1:{s:5:"metas";a:3:{s:9:"reference";s:2:"fr";s:12:"gestionnaire";s:0:"";s:7:"langues";a:2:{s:2:"en";a:0:{}s:2:"ru";a:0:{}}}}', 'non', 'non', 0, '', 'non', 'non', 'non', '', 'fa9e67d7bb9ddcf5b7010dc983e2feca'),
(2260, 2082, 'MICROBLOG', 'http://files.spip.org/spip-zone/microblog.png', '001.002.005', '0.1.0', '[2.1.0;3.0.99]', '2.1,3.0', '<multi>\n			[fr]Envoyer des micro-messages vers les plateformes status.net, twitter (via l''API oAuth), spip.org etc. Fournit une fonction <code>microblog($statut, $user, $pass, $service);</code>.\n	\nUtilise la librairie [twitteroauth->http://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth] d''Abraham Williams pour l''API oAuth de Twitter.\n			[en]Send micromessages to the microblogging platforms like status.net, twitter (via l''API oAuth), spip.org etc. Provides a function <code>microblog($statut, $user, $pass, $service);</code>.\n	\nUses the library [twitteroauth->http://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth] of Abraham Williams for the Twitter oAuth API.\n		</multi>', 'a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:3:"nom";s:16:"Fil © 2009-2012";s:3:"url";s:0:"";s:4:"mail";s:0:"";}}', '', 'a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:3:"nom";s:6:"LGPL 3";s:3:"url";s:41:"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0.html";}}', '', 'http://contrib.spip.net/Microblog', '', '', 'stable', 4, 'a:3:{s:9:"necessite";a:0:{}s:9:"librairie";a:0:{}s:7:"utilise";a:0:{}}', '2014-09-14 20:53:11', '2014-09-14 20:53:11', 1, 'microblog.zip', 74527, '2015-12-23 14:09:00', '_plugins_/microblog', 'a:1:{s:9:"microblog";a:3:{s:9:"reference";s:2:"fr";s:12:"gestionnaire";s:0:"";s:7:"langues";a:1:{s:2:"en";a:0:{}}}}', 'non', 'non', 0, '', 'non', 'non', 'non', '', '48b708712b82a9eddede43b3e2ee1a5a'),
(2261, 2083, 'MIGRATEUR', 'http://files.spip.org/spip-zone/migrateur.png', '003.000.007', '', '[2.1.0;3.1.*]', '2.1,3.0,3.1', '<multi>\n[fr]Migrateur permet de scripter des migrations complexes et répétitives. Il s''adresse à un public averti et nécessite que le site source et le site cible soient sur le même serveur.\n</multi>', 'a:2:{i:1;a:3:{s:3:"nom";s:12:"Cyril Marion";s:3:"url";s:0:"";s:4:"mail";s:0:"";}i:2;a:3:{s:3:"nom";s:19:"Matthieu Marcillaud";s:3:"url";s:0:"";s:4:"mail";s:0:"";}}', '', 'a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:"nom";s:7:"GNU/GPL";s:3:"url";s:0:"";}}', '', 'http://contrib.spip.net/4477', '', '', 'dev', 2, 'a:3:{s:9:"necessite";a:0:{}s:9:"librairie";a:0:{}s:7:"utilise";a:0:{}}', '2015-07-13 17:47:00', '2015-07-13 17:47:00', 1, 'migrateur.zip', 158605, '2015-12-23 14:08:48', '_plugins_/migrateur/trunk', 'a:1:{s:9:"migrateur";a:2:{s:9:"reference";s:2:"fr";s:12:"gestionnaire";s:0:"";}}', 'non', 'non', 0, '', 'non', 'non', 'non', '', '1ff7e1c234aedda07ac092ea088cfa04'),
